text:
Destiny’s Trials of Osiris Returns October 16th, Bungie Details Changes 
Published By: Gamerant.com - Today 
Bungie announces the wait is almost over for the fan-favorite Trials of Osiris PvP event, which will return to Destiny with some new changes...
